text: El-Hadi Laameche (born March 5, 1990) is an Algerian marathon runner. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's marathon but did not finish the race. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Algerian male marathon runners Category:Olympic athletes of Algeria Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Algerian male long-distance runners
